#GraffGems • The central motif of the Sun + Moon high jewellery necklace was created in bas-relief, with layers of diamonds creating a remarkable sense of volume.
 
“Richly sculptural, we also set the pavé and calibré cut diamonds at opposing angles to exaggerate the depth of the motif, with the reverse – which mirrors the arches of the Graff Gateway motif – just as beautiful and interesting as the front.” Sam Sherry, Atelier General Manager.
 
 
#FallinLoveWithGraff
#GraffDiamonds
#GraffTribal

#FallinLoveWithGraff
#GraffDiamonds
#GraffTribal
